  </section>

  <!-- Problem -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-10 text-gray-300" id="problem">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#47C6A2] mb-4">Why Most Resumes Fail ATS Screening</h2>
    <p><strong>99% of Fortune 500 companies</strong> use ATS to scan resumes in just <strong>7.4 seconds</strong>. If your resume isn‚Äôt optimized, it‚Äôs likely never seen by a human recruiter.</p>
