    <p class="mb-4">You spend hours perfecting your resume, but it never reaches recruiters. Less qualified candidates move ahead while you‚Äôre stuck waiting.</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
      <li>The average job search takes <strong>5‚Äì6 months without ATS optimization</strong>.</li>
